%% Diagram: Service Worker lifecycle states and transitions
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false, 'flowchart': {'htmlLabels': false}}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Parsed: register()
    Parsed --> Installing: install event
    Installing --> Installed: install handler resolved
    Installing --> Redundant: install rejected
    Installed --> Waiting: previous SW still controls clients
    Installed --> Activating: no previous SW OR skipWaiting()
    Waiting --> Activating: clients close OR skipWaiting()
    Activating --> Activated: activate handler resolved
    Activated --> Idle: nothing to do
    Idle --> Running: fetch / sync / message event
    Running --> Idle: handler resolved
    Idle --> Terminated: browser frees memory
    Terminated --> Running: next event wakes worker
    Activated --> Redundant: replaced by newer SW
    Redundant --> [*]
